{"tid":1709384,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"央視評論指暴徒越來越喪心病狂　只能以最嚴厲執法回敬","createTime":"2019-11-12T01:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T02:23:25.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f7236d602cdc81828a877678bfd562c4cf259605","tid":1709384,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:11:56.000Z","msg":"央視發表評論員文章，指香港暴徒從企圖搶走警槍，到向市民淋潑易燃液體並點燃，可見暴徒變本加厲，越來越無法無天，越來越喪心病狂，只能以最嚴厲的執法回敬。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，事實證明，這場鬥爭已經是關乎香港前途命運的生死保衛戰，到了退無可退的地步，依法制止及懲治暴力活動，是維護廣大民眾福祉，是對香港負責，是保障香港未來。<br />\n<br />\n文章強調，止暴制亂仍然是香港最重要任務，亦是行政、立法、司法機關的共同責任，他們旗幟鮮明地支持警隊嚴正及果斷執法，確保香港社會治安及市民生命財產安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491477-20191112.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491477-20191112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=393550a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491477-20191112.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=73119935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491477-20191112.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"07f48ba20dfab9a34d5a56f5d995918052e046bd","tid":1709384,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:12:47.000Z","msg":"其實咩叫 評論員文章.... 好難聽個名"},{"pid":"93c7bc1c0db88ad1715210f4122b129af090a107","tid":1709384,"uid":123317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:12:53.000Z","msg":"即係冇哂招"},{"pid":"123471bc4ed9f8f023e93b9c9b8080f73713ae35","tid":1709384,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:13:49.000Z","msg":"&quot;嚴厲&quot;係work既話 <br />\n612之後就應該靜晒啦"},{"pid":"d5c1a27844ad833f3b8717a074af1ca5fdcb4740","tid":1709384,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07f48ba20dfab9a34d5a56f5d995918052e046bd","tid":1709384,"uid":181789,"like":0